      <prop type="x-translation-ref">隰有萇楚.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>隰有萇楚，猗儺其枝。夭之沃沃，樂子之無知。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>In the low wet grounds is the carambola tree;
Soft and pliant are its branches,
With the glossiness of tender beauty.
I should rejoice to be like you, 0 tree, without consciousness.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
